videos.description: Villanova hustles to win a loose ball, then passes all around the perimeter to get an open look for Saddiq Bey, who knocks down the 3-ball.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Villanova's great ball movement sets up open 3) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Villanova's great ball movement sets up open 3

videos.description: Jeremiah Robinson-Earl grabs the rebound and throws an outlet to Cole Swider, who quickly dishes to Saddiq Bey for the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Nova pushes pace for transition triple) 2019/11/16 ESHEET
